title: SPY Presents: Skinner's Alternate Reality
description: Sacramento-based illustrator, painter and muralist Skinner recently paid sunny So Cal a visit for his new show, "The Butcher Kings," at Gallery 1988 Melrose in Los Angeles. If you aren't familiar with under-the-radar artist and SPY collaborator Skinner, you will be, as his new goggle is currently wreaking havoc on shop shelves globally. Never ones to back-down from the threat of a good time, we took a trip up to L.A. to show our boy some love, present him his new collaboration Trevor goggle and hand deliver him a pair of the new SPY Bowery sunglasses. Stay tuned—this is only the beginning of a hellish ride with our enigmatic friend. Check-out spyoptic.com for more info about the SPY + Skinner collab.
